Notes: WIAC Tournament - Second Round...Fourth-seed UWO, the three-time defending
tournament champion, advances to semifinal round to play at top-seed
UW-Whitewater (22-3) on Feb. 23...UWO won 11th straight tournament game and
extended home winning streak to 17 games...UWO got 14 points from Jorgensen.
